      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Bride of Charlie - Episode 4\n## War With Iran & The Kazerian Empire\n\n### Opening: Charlie's Assassination Theory\n\n\"It is my personal belief that that is the very reason they colluded to have that obstacle eventually removed just months later.\n\nI believe on the basis of evidence that Charlie's murder was likely a **very sophisticated military operation** that was meant to **galvanize American support behind Israel**.\"\n\n### Main Story Arcs\n\n**1. Charlie vs. Neocons on Iran**\n- Charlie stopped Trump from Iran war at White House\n- \"Operation Midnight Hammer\" - limited strike agreement\n- BB and Zionists wanted full-scale war\n- 31-year-old Charlie was obstacle to their plans\n\n**2. Turning Point's Betrayal**\n- McCoy & Blake Neff claim Charlie would support war\n- Using \"ghost of Charlie\" to manipulate opinion\n- Erica scheduled to record with BB & Ben Shapiro\n- \"She loved Charlie like LBJ loved JFK\"\n\n**3. The Vince Lombardi Bombshell**\n- Charlie states on camera: Lorie is \"direct descendant\" of Vince Lombardi\n- Super Bowl trophy named after Lombardi\n- Paraphernalia all over Charlie's house\n- Grandmother: Angelina **Lombardo** Abbis\n\n**4. Bible Study Timeline Collapse**\n- 2008: 8 months locked in room studying Bible\n- 2016: First time reading Bible cover to cover with friend\n- Multiple contradictory accounts\n- \"Pathological liar\" or \"programming\"?"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "55555555-5555-4555-8555-555555555555",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Charlie's Iran Position vs TPUSA",
      "position": {
        "x": 600,
        "y": -220
      },
