      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Erica Still Close To Rick Today\n\n### The Universal Studios Visit\n\n**December 1st, 2018:**\n- Erica documented trip to Universal Studios\n- With her mother Lorie (\"always with Lorie\")\n- Instagram stories saved\n- Shows **\"Uncle Rick\"**\n\n**Rick's Position:**\n- High up at Universal Studios\n- \"Makes me wonder if that could have been a potential pathway for her to win Miss Arizona in 2012\"\n\n### The NBC Universal Connection\n\n**2012 Timing:**\n- NBC Universal and Trump split ownership of Miss Universe pageant\n- Rick working at Universal Studios\n- Erica wins Miss Arizona 2012\n\n**Quote:** \"I have no proof of that. I'm just saying that's an interesting tie that Rick is working over at Universal Studios.\"\n\n### The Gangster Observation\n\n**Candace's Take:**\n\n\"That's one of my favorite things about gangsters.\n\nMost people if they have a traffic ticket, they got to show it. They got a record. 'Oh gosh, this is going to hurt my chances of getting a job.'\n\nUrban Beck kind of a big deal. **$34 million went missing and he's at the top of Universal Studios.**\n\nJust incredible.\n\nI don't know. Feel like if my brother was the Zodiac Killer or something, I probably wouldn't be able to go down and work for Disney or Universal Studios.\"\n\n### The Family Proximity Issue\n\n**Candace's Standard:**\n\"For some people, proximity to criminals, non-starter. That's how I would say I live my life.\n\nBeing close with your brother who tried to kill your sister probably wouldn't be my thing.\n\n**Both Lori and Erica. It's fine.**\""
      }
    },
