          }
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## The Remaining Divorce Documents\n\n### \"Simply a Clerical Error\"\n\n**The Debunker Narrative:**\nInitial filing was just clerical error listing Erica's birthday as November 22nd instead of 20th.\n\n**Candace's Response:**\n\"To be clear, there was no cleric involved. It's a document filed by Lori, sitting down with her lawyer, reviewing it with her lawyer.\n\nWhen you go into a courtroom, you have to swear the statements are true.\"\n\n### The Complete Document Trail\n\n**1995 & 1996:** Two separation agreements\n- Birthday: November 22nd, 1988\n\n**January 8, 1998:** Joint shared parenting plan\n- Filled in by hand\n- \"Someone tried to edit it by hand\"\n- Birthday: November 22nd, 1988\n\n**September 10, 1998:** Amendment to child support\n- \"Most egregious of all filings\"\n- **No notary**\n- **No judge signing off**\n- \"Lori was just like going off of vibes there\"\n- \"Her attorney was like, 'This is a bridge too far even for me'\"\n- Signatures between Lori and Kent \"very similar\"\n- \"Kent waived off his rights without a notary\"\n- Birthday: November 22nd, 1988\n\n**November 10, 1998:** Final decree\n- Erica's name typed in\n- Birthday: November 22nd, 1988\n\n**January 1999:** Medical child support document\n- Requires consent of health insurance (Aetna)\n- \"Actually, the only date that really matters here is Erica's birthday. You want to make sure you have the right kid.\"\n- Birthday: November 22nd, 1988\n\n**July 2004:** Kent defaults on child support\n- Enforcement agency records default plus Erica's birthday\n- Birthday: November 22nd, 1988\n\n**2007:** Child support emancipation (Erica turns 18)\n- \"Nobody got anything wrong in 2007. Fantastic year.\"\n- Birthday: November 22nd, 1988\n\n### The Point\n\n\"Apparently, there isn't a clerk across **10 years** that can type in 20 as opposed to 22.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Psychopaths Are Created, Not Born",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1460
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 600,
      "color": "#880e4f",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
