        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Elizabeth Lane's Thesis Revisited\n\n### The Psychopath Theory\n\n**Elizabeth Lane argued:**\nErica Kirk might be a psychopath, not a sociopath.\n\n**What Disturbs Us:**\n- Words coming out of her mouth\n- But expressions are not right\n- Actions are not right\n- Body has natural defense system\n- We pull back before we can register why\n\n**Even Supporters:**\n- \"I can't watch her\"\n- \"I can't listen to her\"\n- \"I hope she does well, but I don't want to watch this\"\n- They can't watch her either\n\n### Candace Builds Upon This\n\n**Critical Point:**\n\"Psychopaths are not born. They are **created**. Typically, they are created in their youth.\n\nIf the work of Sigmund Freud, who rather obsessed himself with creating psychopaths, is to be believed...\n\nI would respectfully submit to you all that **Erica's childhood is actually the most important piece of the puzzle**.\"\n\n### The Lorie Instagram Posts\n\n**The Timing:**\n- Erica didn't post her mother for years\n- Suddenly moves to post mother in vulnerable sick position\n- **2-3 days before Charlie's assassinated**\n\n**Why This Matters:**\n\"That registers to me as emotionally manipulative.\n\nI don't know many people who would move to curate an Instagram reel of their mother in that condition.\n\nMost of all, I don't know many people who would want or allow them to.\n\n**That tells us also something's not right with Lori.**\n\nWhy would you want someone curating these moments of you and putting it online as if to say, 'Hey, don't even look here'?\n\nLeaking to people without any clarity. 'I heard her mother has cancer.' They're putting this out here without any clarity.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
