        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Charlie's Shocking Revelation\n\n### The Charlie Kirk Show Clip\n\n**Someone emailed Candace:**\n\"I listened to Charlie's podcast... regarding his thoughts on past Super Bowls. Charlie was speaking about the Green Bay Packers and mentioned that **Erica's mom is a direct line to the Lombardi family**.\n\nI thought this might be an interesting piece to your puzzle.\"\n\n### Who Is Vince Lombardi?\n\n**Most Famous American Football Coach:**\n- Of all time\n- Green Bay Packers\n- Won first Super Bowl ever\n- **Super Bowl trophy named after him: The Lombardi Trophy**\n\n### Charlie's Exact Words\n\n**On Air:**\n\"The Packers won the first Super Bowl. You know, my wife Erica is from the Lombardi family.\"\n\n**Guest:** \"Really? Is that right? Seriously?\"\n\n**Charlie:** \"Yeah. That's royal. Her mom's a Lombardi. Literally, isn't that insane? That's royal.\"\n\n**Guest:** \"Like direct bloodline? Like lineal descent from Vince?\"\n\n**Charlie:** \"Wow. That's crazy. Yeah. We have all this Packer stuff at our house.\"\n\n**Guest:** \"I didn't know that.\"\n\n**Charlie:** \"And I'm from a huge Bears family, so I don't know.\"\n\n### Candace's Analysis\n\n**First Thought:**\n\"Charlie's not lying because take it from me, **he's not dumb enough to tell a lie that big on camera**.\n\nHe knows they will fact check him real quick.\"\n\n**Second Thought:**\n\"Is Erica lying? I would rank that as a strong possibility.\n\nWere it not for the fact that Charlie said **they had a ton of Vince Lombardi's paraphernalia around the house**.\"\n\n### What \"Direct Descendant\" Means\n\n\"Charlie is not known for hyperbole. He knows words have meaning.\n\nA **direct descendant** therefore would mean that Lori is **Vince Lombardi's offspring**.\n\nThat's really our only option here given the ages.\n\nLori is born in 1950.\""
      }
    },
