            "side": "top",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## \"A Little Bit of History\"\n\n### The Khazarian Empire\n\n**8th, 9th, 10th Century:**\n- Existed\n- Then \"magically disappeared, magically\"\n- Turkic tribe\n- Nomadic tribe\n- **Mass converted to Judaism**\n- Not ethnically Jewish\n- \"They mixed in with people who are actually Jews\"\n\n### \"They Call This A Conspiracy\"\n\n**The Claim:**\nPeople in Israel now are the Khazarian mafia\n\n**But:**\n\"If you read books that were printed **in Israel by the Israelis**, they themselves declared that they were Khazari.\n\nAbraham Pollock as an example:\n- Wrote a book\n- Did all the research\n- **Awarded for his research**\n- Said, 'Hey, we're that tribe. We are the Turks that mass converted to Judaism.'\n- Then he was told it was inconvenient after 1948\n- 'Oh no, no, no. We're claiming we're the original Jews from the Bible. So let's just get rid of all this research.'\"\n\n### The Italian Mafia Was Actually Jewish\n\n**Hollywood Founded By Jewish Gangs:**\n- Universal, MGM\n- \"There's no hiding that, okay? There's no denying it.\"\n- Initially carnies running carnivals\n- \"Wow people with illusions - the occultists\"\n- \"Let's do this on larger scale. Let's do movies.\"\n- \"Get people to pour into cathedrals. Put on a show.\"\n\n**The Carnival Connection:**\n\"That's why you go to a carnival with so much magic and illusion.\n\nMovies are another illusory trick. It captures your imagination. It captures your emotions and it's **almost never based in reality**.\"\n\n### The Real Story\n\n**Prevailing Narrative:**\n\"Italian mafia just for no reason partnered with Meyer Lansky and Bugsy Siegel.\n\nThe Italian and then the Jewish mafia got together. No.\"\n\n**Reality:**\n\"Yes. The Italian mafia, they spoke Italian.\n\nBut that's because they **immigrated to Italy after revolutions**.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "eeeeeeee-eeee-4eee-8eee-eeeeeeeeeeee",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "The Pale of Settlement & Assassinations",
      "position": {
        "x": 1180,
        "y": 1260
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 820,
      "color": "#4a148c",
      "ports": [
