      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## New Confirmations & Mysteries\n\n### St. Ursula Villa Confirmed\n\n**Kindergarten 1994-1995:**\n- Photo found\n- **Before** she went to Arizona\n- Name spelled with **C** (\"another clerical error\")\n\n**2000-2002:** Still missing\n- \"No one with a yearbook has been able to confirm her\"\n- \"Those years are still technically missing\"\n- \"Maybe we had it in reverse\"\n\n### Regis Basketball Confirmed\n\n**2007-2008 Season:**\n- Photo from December 2007 with team members\n- But did NOT play\n- Stats still up showing only 2007-2008\n- No newspaper mentions\n- **Team members confirm she did not play 2008 season**\n\n**Despite:**\n- Erica claiming \"multiple times\" she played two years\n- Notre Dame alumni packet says two years\n\n### The Missing 8 Months Mystery\n\n**Comment Theory:**\n\"Many of you guys thought that she went to have a baby.\n\n'In my day when someone went away for eight months, it's cuz they got knocked up and they had to go away.'\n\nI've seen no evidence of that.\"\n\n**Candace's Theory:**\n\"I'm just going to keep following the facts and following Erica's words.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b2b2b2b2-b2b2-4b2b-8b2b-b2b2b2b2b2b2",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Bible Study Timeline Collapse",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 2780
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 720,
      "color": "#1565c0",
      "ports": [
        {
